The paper focuses on automated program repair, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The approach proposed in the paper involves mining relevant fix patterns, which involves analyzing code syntax and semantics, suggesting that the paper may also fall under programming languages (cs.PL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories.
